{"image_id": "DGX_2015_page_52", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "48", "bbox": [627.1, 1563.2, 647.9, 1590.6]}, {"text": "SELECTED HISTORICAL FINANCIAL DATA OF OUR COMPANY", "bbox": [324.2, 85.1, 951.6, 108.1]}, {"text": "The following table summarizes selected historical financial data of our Company and our subsidiaries at the dates and", "bbox": [179.2, 132.7, 1174.4, 160.0]}, {"text": "for each of the periods presented.  We derived the selected historical financial data for the years 2011 through 2015 from the", "bbox": [104.2, 157.7, 1144.4, 185.0]}, {"text": "audited consolidated financial statements of our Company.  During the fourth quarter of 2012, we sold our OralDNA salivary", "bbox": [104.2, 182.7, 1152.9, 210.0]}, {"text": "diagnostics business, and committed to a plan to sell our HemoCue diagnostic products business.  The sale of HemoCue was", "bbox": [104.2, 207.7, 1147.6, 235.0]}, {"text": "completed in April 2013.  During the third quarter of 2006, we completed the wind down of NID, a test kit manufacturing", "bbox": [104.2, 232.7, 1124.3, 260.0]}, {"text": "subsidiary.  As a result, the operations for HemoCue, OralDNA and NID have been classified as discontinued operations for all", "bbox": [104.2, 257.7, 1168.0, 285.0]}, {"text": "periods presented.  At December 31, 2012, the assets and liabilities of HemoCue were reported as held for sale.  The selected", "bbox": [104.2, 282.7, 1150.9, 310.0]}, {"text": "historical financial data is only a summary and should be read together with the audited consolidated financial statements and", "bbox": [104.2, 307.7, 1155.5, 335.0]}, {"text": "related notes of our Company and management's discussion and analysis of financial condition and results of operations", "bbox": [104.2, 332.7, 1109.5, 360.0]}, {"text": "included elsewhere in this Annual Report on Form 10-K.", "bbox": [104.2, 357.7, 583.2, 385.0]}, {"text": "Year Ended December 31,", "bbox": [787.8, 403.7, 998.2, 424.5]}, {"text": "2015", "